{"tid":1281680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我有個錯誤的觀念，但或者可以幫到你","createTime":"2019-07-03T10:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T14:15:18.000Z","uid":105042,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d29535ef8b202cada3bfa3d57a3c1064ede0af07","tid":1281680,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:52:52.000Z","msg":"如果你好傷心，好悲哀，呢啲都係正常，但係記住，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">傷害係人地帶比你，點解仲要傷害自己？</span><br />\n<br />\n既然係<span style=\"color: red;\">人地嘅錯</span>，點解仲要自己承受所有傷害？我知道仇恨係唔啱，但<span style=\"color: red;\">化悲為憤</span>或者可以令你好過啲。因為放下仇恨總比忘記傷痛易得多。<br />\n<br />\n我地嘅抗爭<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好需要你</span></span>，有咩事我地一齊面對！<br />\n<br />\n我係好清楚呢個觀念係唔好嘅，但如果可以令你好過啲，有多丁點動力的話已經好好，之後嘅事再一齊面對。"},{"pid":"c553d67411c2a0dfc139d4f87f804038fcf06375","tid":1281680,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:55:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"571d5728b2cb260ca2a70da8c78885f4b88fa7e3","tid":1281680,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:58:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83884b44d7dd4c6cf8507aa22b985f6cd1d8e897","tid":1281680,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:01:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2057e91ed8fe3c8188fcfc97a58bc7e9fa728d7","tid":1281680,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:04:29.000Z","msg":"&mdash; 輿 論 戰 及 抗 爭 需 知 大 整 合 &mdash;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1281593\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1281593</a>"},{"pid":"31f68e0f527e7ff153638eb7e808dd1b34d8c1d9","tid":1281680,"uid":219570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d78115d69e4ee03235292843fba63a99d64b87","tid":1281680,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:09:55.000Z","msg":"如果你對政府嘅仇恨都改變